author: Jorge Alonso
title: WWE Superstar Paige Reacts To Her Explicit Photos And Videos Being Leaked On The Internet
text:
Paige, Instagram

WWE wrestler Paige is the latest celebrity victim of what is being called the Fappening 2.0 
On Friday, nude photos and sex videos of the WWE superstar quickly made their way on social media which led to her releasing this statement
on Twitter in which she called the leaked photos “personal and private” and claims they were stolen.
Personal and private photos of mine were stolen and unfortunately they were shared publicly without my consent.
— PAIGE (@RealPaigeWWE) March 17, 2017 

Actresses Amanda Seyfried Emma Watson and Rose McGowan have also been subject to similar leaks this week.
